Package: statshouse-api
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, gnuplot-nox, fonts-open-sans
Description: statshouse-api provides HTTP API and frontend for StatsHouse.

Package: statshouse-grafana-plugin
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: statshouse-grafana-plugin provides StatsHouse data source plugin for Grafana.

Package: statshouse-metadata
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: statshouse-metadata provides storage of metadata for StatsHouse.
